<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 1. Pentikost ni bang khan aw Hukdampa,
 Hung kit inla namtin chitin te;
 Kumkhaw pielgal lam mangin a gim ui,
 Puidawk kit inla.

[V2]
 Buoina gam lungzin um sunavak din,
 Hung kithuom in, Na theih na lopi'n;
 Buoina kang thieng dingin mei kuong bangin,
 Thagau hung inla.

[V3]
 2. Thihna huoisie thuoka na tatsate,
 Khawvel pak tana muong denhaw hi;
 Nangin puiin, Na kumkhaw gam lalna,
 Lam mansak te chu.

[V4]
 3. Thagau Thiengtho nunnem hungkit inla,
 Hukdam ngai ui Na cha taimang te'n;
 A kumkhaw hinnau lampi helo a,
 Beimang dingte khu.

[V5]
 4. A ngilh sawt taluou Kraws a Na thawkna,
 A lunguh gilo thim salhvakin;
 A kipahnau pakcha chu muolsak in,
 Na puih theih na'ngin.</lyrics>
<title>Pentikost Ni Bang Khan !</title>
<hymn_number>105</hymn_number>
</song>